everyone else I was of course right away thinking of fancy interfaces with spinning
cubes and what not, and hadn't really given it much thought&nbsp;abot applying&nbsp;it
in an "ordinary" application with some "ordinary" controls. But after reading Bob's
post it really makes sense!
</p>
