<p>
<i>This blog is written directly by the ArcGIS Server Development Team.&nbsp; We are
very excited about the ArcGIS Server 9.2 release.&nbsp; We have so much to share with
the user community.&nbsp;&nbsp;Topics will range from detailed programming information
("What is a page life cycle in the Web ADF?")&nbsp;to GIS methodology ("What is the
best methodology to produce map caches?")&nbsp;for serving spatial data with ArcGIS
Server.&nbsp; One of the key parts to this blog will be the use of an example site.&nbsp;
We intend to post useful entries for our users which are linked directly to examples
that we have built that you can access live from the Internet.</i>
</p>
